<span id="freeTextContainer2767388638353220108">Super short short stories, ranging from 3-10 pages per. Amazingly - I didn&apos;t hit upon one that left me dangling, or feeling incomplete, as some short stories do. Narayan&apos;s writing is ---spicy is the word that comes to mind, like eating hot chilli peppers that wake up every taste bud in your mouth and leave you grabbing for more. Couldn&apos;t put this one down, I found it electrifying.</span>
